5. Software Product Vision
Necessary features to help users easily access and rent a room as soon as possible:
- Searching and view motel detail: give students many options to search like search by sector, by price, by area of room, by max volumn of room, by type of renting
- Rating & Comment: students can rate their current rented-motel. Motel owners can base on supporting comments to fix/develop motel services
- Sychronyze: rooms that are in negotiation will be marked to avoid conflict between students
- Students management: motel owner will have information of students who renting their rooms
Future feature: 
- Payment method: student can deposit online with motel owners through bank account, ATM/internet banking
- Finding pair: students upload their bio if they want to finding pair, other students can be searched by key word
